What you need to know:

World Athletics president Sebastian Coe noted they are aware of the difficulties that sport has faced during the pandemic but many of our member federations have risen to that challenge brilliantly.“We wanted to acknowledge some of the exceptional work they have done to ensure that our sport continues to thrive in these very testing times,’’ said the president. “The commitment and creativity shown by our member federations demonstrates exactly why we are the world’s most global sport and I applaud their efforts.”